<p>
	This beautiful pretty pink candle with glittery hearts on the surface has a lovely sweet and fruity aroma. With its lively top notes of ripe plum and cassis leading towards heart notes of aniseed, warm ginger, cinnamon and exotic jasmine, underscored by vanilla and woody aspects. The candle is blended with pure neroli and mandarin essential oils and burns for approximately 45 hours. When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
